148
00:12:10,090 --> 00:12:11,090
Á!

149
00:12:11,290 --> 00:12:12,290
Hửm?

150
00:12:21,170 --> 00:12:23,110
<FONT COLOR="#FFFF66">DENNIS 2 TUỔI!

